data.description: Motivated Seller! Beautiful custom 4 bedroom 3 bath spacious pool home! No HOA or CDD! City water and City sewer not in a flood zone! This home sits on TWO lots fenced for additional privacy. There is plenty of room including a private office , formal dining and living room, kitchen/ family room combo, dinette and a gourmet kitchen that is bright and open. The kitchen features a center island, granite counter tops, open concept all making this a chef's dream kitchen. Many extra details throughout the home such as tray ceilings, crown molding, built in entertainment centers, sliders, french doors, and central vac system. The large screened in outdoor pool area is perfect for entertaining with plenty of room for outdoor dining and lounging in the sun. In addition the back yard has a separate cement pad that can be used for basketball, grilling, or a back yard fire pit party. In addition, a boat/rv covered port is next to the garage for boat storage or possibly a camper. Great location close to I-75, shopping and restaurants all close by. Short drive to beaches and outdoor activities!
